=======================
Mandriva Control Center
=======================



Basic usage
===========

1. Edit file mcc2/backends/services/com.mandriva.mcc2.Services.service
and change the follow line:

Exec=/home/wiliam/dev/mcc2/mcc2/backends/services/services-mechanism.py

Copy this file to /usr/share/dbus-1/services/

2. Copy mcc2/backends/services/com.mandriva.mcc2.services.policy 
to /usr/share/polkit-1/actions/

3. Copy mcc2/backends/services/com.mandriva.mcc2.Services.conf
to /etc/dbus-1/system.d/
